Margaret Campbell https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Margaret_Campbell 0 Margaret Campbell (April 24, 1883 – June 27, 1939) was an American character actress in silent films. In her later years she was the secretary of the Bahá'í Spiritual Assembly of Los Angeles. Margaret_Campbell ( April_24_,_1883 – June_27_,_1939 ) was an_American_character_actress in silent_films .
